author: jerenkrantz
msg: ra_serf: Handle multiple-directory commits plus deletions on commit; also
handle locally missing files on an update.
(commit_context_t): Add in baseline checkout, plus the checked_in_url.
(dir_context_t): Add our directory checkout with its checked_in_url.
(checkout_dir): Ensure all of our directories in hierarchy are checked out.
(open_root): Remove my confusion over what the real baseline_url is and
ensure that our baseline is checked out at this point.
(open_directory): Note what our checked_in_url would be.
(open_file): Don't use the baseline, but the root's checked_in_url.
(start_merge): Set COLLECTION enum if we see it in the response.
(delete_path): Implement by sending missing tags to server with REPORT.
